GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAI SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi,
18 June, 1977.
28 Jyaistha, 1899(s).
www.av e
The undersigned is directed to state that -
(i) Shri Parkash Singh Badal relinquished
the office of the Minister of Agriculture
and Irrigation (Krishi aur Sinohai Mantri)
with effect from the afternoon of 17th
June, 1977.
(ii) Shri Surjit Singh Barnala aSsumed the
office of the Minister of Agrioulture
and Irrigation (Krishi aur Sinchai
Mantri) with effect from the forenoon
of 18th June, 1977.
(K. Ramiah)
for Cabinet Secretary
To
All Members of the Cabinet.
Copy forwarded to the Deputy Chairman, Flanning Commission
(Up-adhyaksha, Yojana Ayog)/All Members of the Flanning Commission.
Copy forwarded for information to:-
Principal Secretary to the Prime Minister
(Pradhan Mantri ke Pradhan Sachiv).
Joint Sedretary to the Prime Minister
(Pradhan Mantri ke Sanyukt Sachiv).
Special Private Secretary to the Prime Minister
(Pradhan Mantri ke Vishesh Niji Sachiv).
Copy forwarded to:-
Secretary to the President (Rashtrapati ke Sachiv).
Secretary to the Vice-President (Up-Rashtrapati ke Sachiv).
ARumial
(K. Ramiah)
Under Secre tary to the Cabinet.
Copy forwarded to all Secretaries/Additional Secretaries
to the Government of India/Chairman, Railway Board/Secretary,
Election Commission/Seoretary, Union Public Service Commission/
Comptroller and Auditor General of India/Accounts Officer, Pay
& Accounts Office, Cabinet Seoretariat, for information.
